latestPosts.caption:
In December end, I had the pleasure of hosting a magnificent evening for the the launch of the legendary @ritukumarhq ‘s latest Fall/Winter collection - ‘Artistic Flowers’. 

A celebration of tradition and innovation, these stunning designs are sure to be treasured for generations to come. Thank you for having me, Ritu Kumar.

The “Beige Begum Embroidered Suit Set” has become a personal favorite, available now at ri.ritukumar.com. Completing the look with timeless jewelry from @sunita_shekhawat_jaipur —an exquisite polki single line string and studs, adding my unique touch of elegance. Here’s to embracing style, stories, and unforgettable moments!

What do you think of my look? Let me know in the comments!

Makeup by @anushkanaarangmakeup 
Shot by @pixelavid

Radhika, for her brother’s big day 🤍
For event one, the memo was: fun, fresh, and just the right amount of extra ✨
We kept the skin radiant and clean, with a nude lip and rhinestone sparkle on the eyes to add a subtle edge.
Straight hair, glowing skin, and a pop of florals in her outfit, this look was all about effortless elegance with a playful twist 💖
